ploads/2025/01/Fender-Sam@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Fender-Sam@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender)</a>与纽卡斯尔联队合作拍卖卡拉宝杯球衣，筹集的资金将捐献给慈善机构。下面了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sam-fender-people-watching-tour-live-review-3819114">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender) 住在利兹：一代乔迪明星安全进入新时代</a></strong></li></ul><p>新的拍卖让纽卡斯尔联球迷有机会拥有一段足球历史，球队在圣詹姆斯公园赢得卡拉宝杯四分之一决赛时所穿的球衣已正式可供购买。</p><p>这些球衣采用定制设计，旨在纪念这位出生于北希尔兹的歌手、作曲家和吉他手，每件球衣都经过亚历山大·伊萨克 (Alexander Isak)、布鲁诺·吉马良斯 (Bruno Guimarães) 和乔林顿 (Joelinton) 等球员的比赛穿着或签名。</p><p>拍卖所得将捐赠给纽卡斯尔联基金会。这将有利于整个东北部的社区倡议，旨在促进该地区年轻人和家庭的教育、机会、健康和社会包容。 </p><figure id="attachment_3827856" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827856" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827856" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sam-Fender@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Sam Fender X 纽卡斯尔联队球衣" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sam-Fender@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sam-Fender@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sam-Fender@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sam-Fender@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sam-Fender@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sam-Fender@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827856" class="wp-caption-text"> Sam Fender X 纽卡斯尔联队球衣。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>每件衬衫都附有个人数字防伪证书，竞拍现已开始。拍卖将持续到 1 月 19 日，您可以<a href="http://MatchWornShirt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>出价并了解更多信息。</p><p> Fender 的慈善活动是为了庆祝他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-new-single-people-watching-and-teases-album-news-3810920">备受期待的第三张专辑“People Watching”，</a>该专辑将于 2 月 21 日通过 Polydor 分享（<a href="https://samfender.lnk.to/peoplewatching" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。</p><p>这张唱片由 Fender 与他的乐队成员 Dean Thompson 和 Joe Atkinson、制作人 Markus Dravs 以及<a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/the-war-on-drugs">The War On Drugs</a>的 Adam Granduciel 共同制作。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-music-with-the-war-on-drugs-adam-granduciel-3601247">首先暗示，早在 2024 年 3 月，他就一直在与后者合作</a>，与制作人、工程师和其他音乐家一起分享他们在录音室里的镜头。然后，十月 Fender 确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-album-is-finished-and-mastered-3799886">新专辑已经完成并“掌握”</a> 。这将是他自 2021 年第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">《Seventeen Going Under》</a>以来的第一张 LP。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEhnuKVzNMs/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https